{"tid":1372251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盡全力支援前線","createTime":"2019-07-27T11:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T13:52:41.000Z","uid":79974,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4c1e253d5893f58e995d15288811bace31a34f18","tid":1372251,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:37:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>承擔最大風險嘅人，應該享有最大權力</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n好多在場示威者都係大學生，俾人拉左可能一世都做唔到專業人士，我明白大家都好驚，我都好驚前途都會盡廢<br />\n<br />\n但前線呢班人，承受住比我地更大嘅危險之外<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>更加係一直保護緊我地</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我驚，好撚驚，但大家同心嘅話，就應該幾驚都好，都要盡全力支援佢地，唔係叫佢地走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不抱怨，不指責，香港人，一條心</strong></span>"},{"pid":"be01c3f3e5d9d320ed8392a23a8a2c17feed1d26","tid":1372251,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:38:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全力支援前線</strong></span>"},{"pid":"1d37877b86a3b46a6aa17ff9238bcf59999e8dbe","tid":1372251,"uid":68787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:38:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34764f0fb9f60428d94abbb802266d4e563a968b","tid":1372251,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:40:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>團結齊上</strong></span>"},{"pid":"c06b94fe52b000e6fe2bc1969c7f62a60f6bee79","tid":1372251,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:40:34.000Z","msg":"支持前線！<br />\n光復香港！"},{"pid":"74b9b64a40f17dca03dec6087026b2d52da14f4f","tid":1372251,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:33:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>團結不分化</strong></span>"},{"pid":"d4b690df5108e1bbf2c4f779586f4b0eafa19037","tid":1372251,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:42:17.000Z","msg":